25). She was named a 2023 actor to watch by Variety.\n\nOliver made her feature film debut in Saltburn, written and directed by Emerald Fennell. The film premiered at the 50th Telluride Film Festival and went on to be nominated for two Golden Globes and five BAFTA Film Awards. In 2024, she played a supporting role in Justin Kurzel's film The Order, which premiered at the 81st Venice International Film Festival. In November 2024, it was announced that she had been cast as Isabella Linton in Emerald Fennell's next film, Wuthering Heights, an adaptation of the novel of the same name.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Alison Oliver, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Alison Oliver","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"艾莉森·奥利弗（Alison Oliver，1997年6月3日-），爱尔兰女演员。","name":"艾莉森·奥利弗","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"אליסון אוליבר","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"أليسون أوليفر","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Елісон Олівер","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Элисон Оливер","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"艾莉森·奧利弗（Alison Oliver，1997 年 6 月 3 日-），愛爾蘭女演員。","name":"艾莉森·奧利弗","primary":false}}]}},"tv_273275_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1774377012719,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/dY2O6fveRgHyAY5YYmPzy2c9G8t.jpg","created_by":[],"episode_run_time":[],"first_air_date":"2026-02-09","genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"},{"id":35,"name":"Phim Hài"}],"homepage":"https://v.qq.com/x/cover/mzc00200lt2l4ly.h